{"tid":1495293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給文宣組一點小建議","createTime":"2019-08-22T04:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:54:29.000Z","uid":196536,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"18c2a66372e4c5c33bd826eabe3e87f0812ae09d","tid":1495293,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"抗爭運動已經進行兩個幾月，文宣組d貨坦白講一次都無另我地失望過。<br />\n靚到可以搞展覽，不過我留意到大部分文宣都係對準某個行動，或者日程。<br />\n建議可以參考二戰英國咁，整一d思想上既文宣。<br />\nExample<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaTLUdX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaTLUdX.png&h=d1ca4ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以用番，改做做緊野既手足既相（或者受左傷既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hawd279.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHawd279.png&h=85ad6c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n改做前線，文宣組，連儂牆小隊，airdrop小隊，物資組等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmCT28N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmCT28N.png&h=70f4c316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以用番勇武和理非相擁果張相（或有更好提議）<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他例子（五大訴求果d咁大路唔舉啦），如：<br />\n<strong>香港人要懂得憤怒，不可麻木</strong><br />\n和理非加勇武可以凝聚最大民眾支持<br />\n今次許勝不許敗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n思想上文宣少d資料，易入腦，方便廣傳，效果明顯！<br />\n希望文宣組採納，認同請幫推，香港人必將戰勝歸來！"},{"pid":"5d325e2d20589ada21fb8eab452a727124880f75","tid":1495293,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c4144d813fdaf0924ec2e1f204ba2677bf9fa1c","tid":1495293,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429b13e1bcb1b13a56de35f05a99614587c0b3d0","tid":1495293,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大聲傳出去啊！！！<br />\n【我宣布】中秋開始罷工罷到支爆為止<br /